Dear Hiring Team, 

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the Software Development Engineer with Amazon Web Services. I bring over three years of professional experience in full-stack web applications, RAG and AI agents, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY.

